                            <comment id="16056665" author="j.casares" created="Tue, 20 Jun 2017 23:27:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a PR for the single-file fix: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/124&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/124&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16057223" author="rha" created="Wed, 21 Jun 2017 09:14:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, I don&apos;t understand why do you want to remove this setting, it&apos;s still used in trunk:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;$ grep -IRn getMaxValueSize
test/unit/org/apache/cassandra/db/compaction/BlacklistingCompactionsTest.java:86:        maxValueSize = DatabaseDescriptor.getMaxValueSize();
